    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cat Life</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>Have you ever wished you had a cat's life ? It's not as easy as you might imagine ...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>To sum up</strong></h2>An open-world action-adventure game focused on PvE combat, exploration, and survival.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Description of the game</strong></h2>Cat Life is an action-adventure game where you control a cat.<br><br>You play in an open world, alone or with friends in co-op mode, with total freedom of movement: you have the ability to climb on all natural or artificial structures.<br>Survive will not be easy, you will have to feed yourself, resist bad weather, and face many opponents!<br>Progress through the main questline to solve the mystery of the island and unlock all of your character's abilities.<br>Or freely explore the world that opens up to you, as well as the mini-games to discover.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Detailed Content</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An open world of 4 km², a wild island in a temperate biome, with a few inhabited areas<br></li><li>Full freedom of movement, including verticality, with the ability to climb all trees and buildings<br></li><li>Hundreds of NPCs, among a bestiary of 40 types of creatures, friendly or enemy<br></li><li>A series of 40 quests to follow in the main story line<br></li><li>Co-op mode to explore and achieve quests with friends<br></li><li>Timed mini-games, agility courses and more<br></li><li>Day/night cycle, and weather events (rain, snow, storm)<br></li><li>Hidden rewards to discover while exploring the world<br></li><li>An experience mechanism to progress through 50 levels<br></li><li>Survival management : health and energy, but also hunger and thirst</li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
